Author: Rivka90
Text: I fantasize about it. You're not alone.

Author: HausDeKittehs
Text: Well, I have a literal terror of losing control and eating huge amounts of food. I wouldn't say that watching huge amounts being eaten make me hungry, but seeing good food makes me hungry.  I don't fast anymore, but when I did I wouldn't look at magazines or watch TV because seeing food would make me hungry. To this day (mostly recovered) I HATE HATE cooking shows.
